---
---

<section class="terminal-section" id="terminal">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal-glitch">
      <h2 class="section-title">Live <span class="gradient-text">Terminal</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A real shell into my resume. Try <code style="color:var(--accent-1);background:rgba(99,102,241,0.1);padding:0.15em 0.4em;border-radius:4px;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:0.85em">help</code> to explore.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="live-terminal reveal-scale">
      <div class="term-chrome">
        <button class="td red" id="termClose" aria-label="Close terminal" title="Close"></button>
        <button class="td yellow" id="termMinimize" aria-label="Minimize terminal" title="Minimize"></button>
        <button class="td green" id="termMaximize" aria-label="Maximize terminal" title="Maximize"></button>
        <span class="term-title" id="termTitle">hiren@hkpanchani.dev ~ %</span>
        <button class="term-tab-btn" id="termNewTab" aria-label="New tab" title="New tab">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        </button>
        <button class="term-settings-btn" id="termSettingsBtn" aria-label="Terminal settings">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v2M12 21v2M4.22 4.22l1.42 1.42M18.36 18.36l1.42 1.42M1 12h2M21 12h2M4.22 19.78l1.42-1.42M18.36 5.64l1.42-1.42"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="term-settings" id="termSettings">
          <div class="ts-group">
            <span class="ts-label">Theme</span>
            <div class="ts-row">
              <button class="ts-theme active" data-ttheme="dark">Dark</button>
              <button class="ts-theme" data-ttheme="matrix">Matrix</button>
              <button class="ts-theme" data-ttheme="retro">Retro</button>
              <button class="ts-theme" data-ttheme="ocean">Ocean</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ts-group">
            <span class="ts-label">Font</span>
            <div class="ts-row">
              <button class="ts-font active" data-tfont="mono">Mono</button>
              <button class="ts-font" data-tfont="fira">Fira</button>
              <button class="ts-font" data-tfont="hack">Hack</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ts-group">
            <span class="ts-label">Size</span>
            <div class="ts-row">
              <button class="ts-size" data-tsize="sm">S</button>
              <button class="ts-size active" data-tsize="md">M</button>
              <button class="ts-size" data-tsize="lg">L</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ts-group">
            <span class="ts-label">Glow</span>
            <div class="ts-row">
              <button class="ts-toggle active" data-tglow="on">On</button>
              <button class="ts-toggle" data-tglow="off">Off</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="term-output" id="termOutput">
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">neofetch</span></div>
        <div class="term-line">&nbsp;</div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">hiren</span><span class="t-system">@</span><span class="t-accent">hkpanchani.dev</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-system">─────────────────────────────</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">OS:</span>          <span class="t-val">AWS us-west-2 (primary) + DR</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">Uptime:</span>      <span class="t-val" id="liveUptime"></span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">Shell:</span>       <span class="t-val">bash + terraform + helm</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">WM:</span>          <span class="t-val">Kubernetes (EKS 1.27→1.36)</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">Packages:</span>    <span class="t-val">44 terraform modules</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">CPU:</span>         <span class="t-val">5 EKS clusters · 60+ microservices</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">Memory:</span>      <span class="t-val">8 Aurora clusters · 3 Kafka</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">Disk:</span>        <span class="t-val">73 S3 buckets · 160 ECR repos</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">Network:</span>     <span class="t-val">5 VPCs · hub-and-spoke</span></div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-key">Throughput:</span>  <span class="t-val">6B+ emails/year</span></div>
        <div class="term-line">&nbsp;</div>
        <div class="term-line"><span class="t-system">Type <span class="t-cmd">help</span> to see available commands.</span></div>
        <div class="term-line">&nbsp;</div>
      </div>
      <div class="term-input-row">
        <span class="t-prompt">$</span>
        <input type="text" class="term-input" id="termInput" placeholder="Type a command..." autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="term-reopen" id="termReopen">▸ Reopen Terminal</button>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .terminal-section {
    padding-top: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .live-terminal {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .term-chrome {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    position: relative;
  }

  .td {
    width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%;
    border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0;
    transition: all 0.15s; position: relative;
  }
  .td:hover { transform: scale(1.2); }
  .td.red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .td.red:hover { background: #ff3b30; }
  .td.yellow { background: #febc2e; }
  .td.yellow:hover { background: #f5a623; }
  .td.green { background: #28c840; }
  .td.green:hover { background: #1db954; }

  /* Close/minimize/maximize icons on hover */
  .td:hover::after {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 8px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  }
  .td.red:hover::after { content: '×'; font-size: 10px; }
  .td.yellow:hover::after { content: '−'; }
  .td.green:hover::after { content: '+'; font-size: 9px; }

  .term-title { margin-left: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-muted); flex: 1; }

  .term-tab-btn {
    width: 24px; height: 24px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 4px; color: var(--text-muted);
    cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s;
    background: none; border: none; padding: 0;
  }
  .term-tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text-primary); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }

  /* Terminal states */
  .live-terminal.minimized .term-output,
  .live-terminal.minimized .term-input-row { display: none; }
  .live-terminal.minimized { border-radius: var(--radius-md); }

  .live-terminal.maximized {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 500;
    max-width: 100%;
    border-radius: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .live-terminal.maximized .term-output { max-height: calc(100vh - 90px); }

  .live-terminal.closed { display: none; }

  /* Reopen button (shown when closed) */
  .term-reopen {
    display: none;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-1);
    background: rgba(99,102,241,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .term-reopen:hover { background: rgba(99,102,241,0.15); border-color: var(--accent-1); }
  .term-reopen.visible { display: inline-flex; }

  .term-output {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    max-height: 400px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  .term-line {
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: inherit;
    line-height: inherit;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .t-prompt { color: var(--accent-3); font-weight: 700; }
  .t-cmd { color: var(--accent-1); font-weight: 600; }
  .t-system { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .t-key { color: var(--accent-2); font-weight: 600; }
  .t-val { color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .t-heading { color: var(--accent-1); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .t-accent { color: var(--accent-3); }
  .t-error { color: #f43f5e; }
  .t-success { color: #22c55e; }
  .t-gold { color: #eab308; }
  .t-link {
    color: var(--accent-3);
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15);
    transition: all 0.15s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .t-link:hover {
    color: #fff;
    background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.4);
  }

  .term-input-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  .term-input {
    flex: 1;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    caret-color: var(--accent-1);
  }

  .term-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); opacity: 0.5; }

  /* ── Settings button ── */
  .term-settings-btn {
    margin-left: auto;
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: all 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .term-settings-btn:hover { color: var(--text-primary); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }

  /* ── Settings panel ── */
  .term-settings {
    position: absolute;
    top: 42px;
    right: 8px;
    width: 200px;
    background: rgba(15, 15, 22, 0.97);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    z-index: 10;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(0.97);
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  }
  .term-settings.open {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    pointer-events: all;
  }
  .ts-group { margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .ts-group:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .ts-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .ts-row { display: flex; gap: 4px; }
  .ts-theme, .ts-font, .ts-size, .ts-toggle {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 4px 6px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ts-theme:hover, .ts-font:hover, .ts-size:hover, .ts-toggle:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .ts-theme.active, .ts-font.active, .ts-size.active, .ts-toggle.active {
    background: rgba(99,102,241,0.12);
    border-color: var(--accent-1);
    color: var(--accent-1);
  }

  /* ── Terminal themes ── */
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] {
    background: rgba(0, 20, 0, 0.8);
    border-color: rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.15);
  }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .t-prompt { color: #00ff41; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .t-cmd { color: #00ff41; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .t-key { color: #00cc33; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .t-val { color: #88cc88; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .t-accent { color: #00ff41; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .t-heading { color: #00ff41; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .t-system { color: #337733; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .term-chrome { background: rgba(0, 20, 0, 0.6); border-bottom-color: rgba(0,255,65,0.1); }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="matrix"] .term-input-row { background: rgba(0, 20, 0, 0.4); border-top-color: rgba(0,255,65,0.08); }

  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] {
    background: rgba(40, 20, 0, 0.85);
    border-color: rgba(255, 176, 0, 0.15);
  }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .t-prompt { color: #ffb000; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .t-cmd { color: #ffb000; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .t-key { color: #ff8c00; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .t-val { color: #ccaa66; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .t-accent { color: #ffb000; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .t-heading { color: #ffb000; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .t-system { color: #886644; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .term-chrome { background: rgba(40, 20, 0, 0.6); border-bottom-color: rgba(255,176,0,0.1); }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="retro"] .term-input-row { background: rgba(40, 20, 0, 0.4); border-top-color: rgba(255,176,0,0.08); }

  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] {
    background: rgba(0, 15, 30, 0.85);
    border-color: rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.15);
  }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .t-prompt { color: #00b4d8; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .t-cmd { color: #48cae4; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .t-key { color: #0096c7; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .t-val { color: #90e0ef; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .t-accent { color: #48cae4; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .t-heading { color: #48cae4; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .t-system { color: #456080; }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .term-chrome { background: rgba(0, 15, 30, 0.6); border-bottom-color: rgba(0,180,216,0.1); }
  .live-terminal[data-ttheme="ocean"] .term-input-row { background: rgba(0, 15, 30, 0.4); border-top-color: rgba(0,180,216,0.08); }

  /* ── Font options ── */
  .live-terminal[data-tfont="fira"] { font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace; }
  .live-terminal[data-tfont="hack"] { font-family: 'Hack', 'Menlo', monospace; }

  /* ── Size options ── */
  .live-terminal[data-tsize="sm"] .term-output { font-size: 0.68rem; }
  .live-terminal[data-tsize="lg"] .term-output { font-size: 0.92rem; }
  .live-terminal[data-tsize="sm"] .term-input { font-size: 0.68rem; }
  .live-terminal[data-tsize="lg"] .term-input { font-size: 0.92rem; }

  /* ── Glow effect ── */
  .live-terminal[data-tglow="on"] .t-cmd,
  .live-terminal[data-tglow="on"] .t-key,
  .live-terminal[data-tglow="on"] .t-heading {
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px currentColor;
  }

  /* Scrollbar inside terminal */
  .term-output::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
  .term-output::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 2px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .term-output { max-height: 300px; font-size: 0.72rem; }
    .term-input { font-size: 0.75rem; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  const input = document.getElementById('termInput') as HTMLInputElement;
  const output = document.getElementById('termOutput')!;
  const history: string[] = [];
  let histIdx = -1;

  const commands: Record<string, () => string> = {
    help: () => `<span class="t-heading">HKPANCHANI(1)              User Commands              HKPANCHANI(1)</span>

<span class="t-key">NAME</span>
    hkpanchani - interactive resume terminal

<span class="t-key">SYNOPSIS</span>
    <span class="t-cmd">command</span> [ENTER]

<span class="t-key">COMMANDS</span>
    <span class="t-cmd">about</span>          Who am I
    <span class="t-cmd">skills</span>         Technical skills by category
    <span class="t-cmd">experience</span>     Work experience summary
    <span class="t-cmd">achievements</span>   Key achievements & projects
    <span class="t-cmd">metrics</span>        Impact by numbers
    <span class="t-cmd">certs</span>          Professional certifications
    <span class="t-cmd">education</span>      Education & awards
    <span class="t-cmd">homelab</span>        Personal infrastructure lab
    <span class="t-cmd">contact</span>        How to reach me
    <span class="t-cmd">stack</span>          Full technology stack
    <span class="t-cmd">neofetch</span>       System information
    <span class="t-cmd">cat resume</span>     Print full resume
    <span class="t-cmd">whoami</span>         Current identity
    <span class="t-cmd">uptime</span>         Professional uptime
    <span class="t-cmd">clear</span>          Clear terminal output

<span class="t-key">NAVIGATION</span>
    <span class="t-val">↑ / ↓</span>          Browse command history

<span class="t-system">hkpanchani.dev                  June 2026                  v2.0</span>`,

    about: () => `<span class="t-heading">Hiren Panchani</span>
<span class="t-key">Role:</span>      <span class="t-val">Solutions Architect — Cloud & Platform Engineering</span>
<span class="t-key">Experience:</span> <span class="t-val">7.5+ years (6.3 cloud/DevOps, 4.3 as Solutions Architect)</span>
<span class="t-key">Focus:</span>     <span class="t-val">Multi-region AWS, Kubernetes, Terraform, Observability</span>
<span class="t-key">Style:</span>     <span class="t-val">I live in terminals, think in YAML, and find peace optimizing cloud bills.</span>

<span class="t-system">➜</span> <a href="#skills" class="t-link">View skills</a> · <a href="/projects" class="t-link">View projects</a> · <a href="/contacts" class="t-link">Get in touch</a>`,

    skills: () => `<span class="t-heading">Technical Skills</span>
<span class="t-key">AWS:</span>          <span class="t-val">EKS, ECS, Lambda, Aurora, MSK, OpenSearch, Bedrock, IAM/KMS, CloudFront, WAF, Route 53</span>
<span class="t-key">Kubernetes:</span>   <span class="t-val">EKS 1.27→1.36, Helm 4, ArgoCD 3, Karpenter, HPA/VPA, IRSA, NetworkPolicy</span>
<span class="t-key">IaC:</span>          <span class="t-val">Terraform (44+ modules), CloudFormation, Helm, Kustomize</span>
<span class="t-key">CI/CD:</span>        <span class="t-val">ArgoCD 3, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, self-hosted runners on Spot EKS</span>
<span class="t-key">Databases:</span>    <span class="t-val">Aurora MySQL 8.0, Aurora PG 16, MongoDB Atlas, ClickHouse, Redis, MSK Kafka</span>
<span class="t-key">Observability:</span><span class="t-val"> Prometheus, Grafana, Loki, Tempo, OpenTelemetry, 40+ dashboards</span>
<span class="t-key">Networking:</span>   <span class="t-val">5 VPCs hub-and-spoke, Cloudflare, Tailscale/Headscale, Nginx</span>
<span class="t-key">Security:</span>     <span class="t-val">SOC 2, ISO 27001/27701, GDPR, SonarQube, VaultWarden, OWASP</span>
<span class="t-key">AI/ML:</span>        <span class="t-val">Bedrock, Titan Embed, OpenSearch k-NN, MCP servers, Ollama</span>
<span class="t-key">Languages:</span>    <span class="t-val">TypeScript, Node.js, Python, Bash, HCL, SQL</span>

<span class="t-system">➜</span> <a href="#skills" class="t-link">Jump to skills section ↗</a>`,

    experience: () => `<span class="t-heading">Professional Experience</span>
<span class="t-key">7.5 years</span> total · <span class="t-key">6.3 years</span> cloud/DevOps · <span class="t-key">4.3 years</span> as Solutions Architect

<span class="t-accent">▸</span> Sole architect and operator of a full multi-region AWS platform
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> Designed 4 isolated environments from scratch (prod/staging/warmup/shared)
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> 60+ microservices across 5 EKS clusters, 8 Aurora clusters, 3 MSK Kafka
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> ~840 production tickets / 50+ epics shipped as one-person platform team
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> Previously: Cloud transformation for 5,000+ users, VPN infrastructure for 500+ remote workers

<span class="t-system">➜</span> <a href="/projects" class="t-link">View all projects ↗</a>`,

    achievements: () => `<span class="t-heading">Key Achievements</span>
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> Greenfield multi-region AWS+EKS platform (4 VPCs, hub-and-spoke, DR region)
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> 9 zero-downtime EKS upgrades (1.27 → 1.36)
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> 44-module Terraform library — new services ship in ~30 lines HCL
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> Full observability stack from scratch (~20% lower TCO vs commercial APM)
<span class="t-accent">▸</span> ~$156K/year cost reduction across 3 cycles (~30% each)
